snippet.title: ｈａｃｋｍｕｄ launch announce trailer
snippet.description:
h a c k m u d is out for almost a decade! Buy it on humble for steam:
https://www.humblebundle.com/store/hackmud
(buying on humble means 100% of sale supports us)

Support our 503(c)(3) non-profit:
https://givebutter.com/QncoAxxT2tdWf3UfJ2x95z25n1HNizxI

h a c k m u d is a text-based multiplayer hacking simulator for keyboard-compatible personal home computers. Crack protected systems and solve puzzles as you explore the abandoned internet of the future. Write scripts to protect your winnings and trick other players. Lose everything. Get it back.
